    class WeatherFrame.SelectionPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Author:
    CS2334. Modified by: Will Booker, David Jones

    Date: 2015-11-06
    Project 4

    This class represents a panel containing the variables that the user will select, including the station, variable, and year(s). It should be possible for a user to select multiple years.
